Method Detail

getCacheUrl

public java.lang.String getCacheUrl()
Returns a url to google's cached version of the page responsible for producing this result. This property may be null indicating that there is no cache, and it might be out of date in cases where the search result has been saved and in the mean time, the cache has gone stale. For best results, this property should not be persisted.

Returns:
a url to google's cached version of the page responsible for producing this result.
